headline: 3 High-Yielding Dividend Stocks to Buy for the Long Haul
summary: Three high-yielding stocks with strong financials that you may want to consider adding to your portfolio today are UnitedHealth Group (NYSE: UNH), Restaurant Brands International (NYSE: QSR), and AT&T (NYSE: T).  Health insurance giant UnitedHealth is the type of stock that can make for an excellent long-term holding in your portfolio.  UnitedHealth's current problems may seem daunting, but years from now, they may be resolved and no longer weigh on its share price.
